These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-1::.
4 different pets are kept: mouse, ferret, guinea-pig, rabbit
1. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
2. the owner of the ferret is somewhere between the owner of the guinea-pig and the owner of the rabbit##7
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Pet   | guinea-pig | ferret | rabbit | mouse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-2::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, grapefruit, radish, grapes
1. the person eating radish is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
2. the person eating radish is somewhere between the person eating grapefruit and the person eating avocado##7
3. the person eating radish is between the person eating grapefruit and the person eating grapes##2

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Food   | avocado | grapes | radish | grapefruit |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-3::.
There 4 different types of food: nectarine, apple, raspberry, mango
1. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person eating apple##1
2. the person eating mango is somewhere between the person eating raspberry and the person eating apple##7
3. the person eating raspberry is somewhere to the right of the person eating mango##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |  2   |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | nectarine | apple | mango | raspberry |

