.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, van, ship, scooter
1. the person driving the scooter is somewhere between the person driving the ship and the person driving the van##7
2. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
3. the person driving the trike is between the person driving the scooter and the person driving the ship##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |   3   |    4    |
| Transport   | ship | trike | scooter | van |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, animation, superhero, scientific
1. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
2. the person watching animation movies is between the person watching spy movies and the person watching scientific movies##2
3. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3
4. the person watching spy movies is somewhere between the person watching superhero movies and the person watching scientific movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |   3   |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | spy | animation | scientific |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: german, polish, egyptian, american
1. the german is somewhere between the american and the polish##7
2. the egyptian is somewhere between the german and the american##7
3. the egyptian is on the left or right of the american##3
4. the egyptian is somewhere to the right of the american##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |     3     |    4    |
| Nationality   | american | egyptian | german | polish |

