.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, soy-milk, juice, hot-chocolate
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking water##7
2. the person drinking juice is somewhere between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person drinking soy-milk##7
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |    2     |   3   |      4      |
| Beverage   | water | hot-chocolate | juice | soy-milk |

