3. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the train##1
4. the person driving the train is somewhere between the person driving the tram and the person driving the trike##7

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4    |
| Transport   | trike | bike | train | tram |

